{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "turn_index": 1, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:33:56.815070+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_007", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨露村的薄雾尚未散尽，老凯恩站在村口的老橡树下，身披褪色的锁子甲，目光如鹰。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_007", "text": "年轻人，村长临终前的话我都听见了。若你真心想挑战恶龙，就证明给我看你的决心。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家首次与老凯恩对话，老凯恩未给予任务，仅表达对勇者决心的考验。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:world_bible:-:-:-:-:e080a416", "20260315_133038_c527e317:location:-:loc_001:-:-:278b9587", "20260315_133038_c527e317:npc_profile:npc_007:-:-:-:d2698d7e"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_133038_c527e317", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "npc_id": "npc_007", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 3, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 16}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "turn_index": 2, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:34:23.672641+00:00", "player_text": "我该怎么证明", "npc_id": "npc_007", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "老凯恩缓缓从腰间解下一枚锈迹斑斑的徽章，目光沉稳。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_007", "text": "去迷雾森林猎三只毒蜘蛛，把毒囊交给猎人巴隆。若你能完成，便算迈出第一步。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [{"quest_id": "quest_side_001", "title": null, "category": null, "status": "active", "objective": null, "guidance": "前往迷雾森林猎杀毒蜘蛛，收集毒囊后交给晨露村的猎人巴隆。", "giver_npc_id": null, "reward_hint": null, "required_items": {}, "reward_items": {}, "collected_items_delta": {}}], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "老凯恩指派玩家执行毒蛛之毒任务，作为对其决心的初步考验。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:world_bible:-:-:-:-:e080a416", "20260315_133038_c527e317:location:-:loc_001:-:-:278b9587", "20260315_133038_c527e317:npc_profile:npc_007:-:-:-:d2698d7e", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:1:-:fea3451b", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:1:-:55a4adab"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_133038_c527e317", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "npc_id": "npc_007", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 5, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 17}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "turn_index": 3, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:34:48.521614+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_002", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨露村的草屋旁，猎人巴隆正擦拭着他的长弓，皮甲上还沾着昨夜狩猎的泥渍。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_002", "text": "嗯？你是那个老凯恩提到的勇者吧。他让我等你带毒蜘蛛毒囊来——三只，少一只都不行。迷雾森林就在村东边，别磨蹭，那鬼地方太阳一高就更难对付了。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家首次与猎人巴隆对话，巴隆确认了毒蛛之毒任务的要求，并指明迷雾森林为任务地点。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:world_bible:-:-:-:-:e080a416", "20260315_133038_c527e317:location:-:loc_001:-:-:278b9587", "20260315_133038_c527e317:npc_profile:npc_002:-:-:-:0516bd76", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:1:-:55a4adab", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:2:-:27220ec4"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:1:-:fea3451b", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:2:-:6d9f5559"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_133038_c527e317", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "npc_id": "npc_002", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 5, "retrieved": 2, "store_total": 18}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "turn_index": 4, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:35:09.163512+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨露村的草屋前，艾拉正低头整理一篮新鲜采摘的药草，阳光透过薄雾洒在她温柔的侧脸上。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "你好，勇者。我是艾拉，村里的草药师。听说你即将前往迷雾森林？那地方毒蛛横行，务必小心。若你需要治疗药水，我可以为你准备一瓶。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {"治疗药水": 1}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家首次与草药师艾拉对话，艾拉主动提供治疗药水，并提醒迷雾森林的危险。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:world_bible:-:-:-:-:e080a416", "20260315_133038_c527e317:location:-:loc_001:-:-:278b9587", "20260315_133038_c527e317:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:cde9ba91", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:1:-:55a4adab", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:2:-:27220ec4", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:3:-:0494063c"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_002:loc_001:3:-:6dc04883", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:1:-:fea3451b", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:2:-:6d9f5559"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_133038_c527e317", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 6, "retrieved": 3, "store_total": 19}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "turn_index": 5, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:35:43.367558+00:00", "player_text": "可以啊", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "艾拉轻轻将一束干枯的月光草放入木箱，抬头望向你，眼中透着关切。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "太好了！我刚熬好一瓶治疗药水，你带上吧。迷雾森林里的毒蛛毒性极强，若被咬伤，立刻服下它。另外……如果你在林中看到银叶草，能带些回来吗？村里的孩子最近咳嗽得厉害，那草是唯一的解药。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {"治疗药水": 1}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "艾拉赠予玩家一瓶治疗药水，并请求玩家在迷雾森林中采集银叶草以救治村中病童。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:world_bible:-:-:-:-:e080a416", "20260315_133038_c527e317:location:-:loc_001:-:-:278b9587", "20260315_133038_c527e317:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:cde9ba91", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_001:loc_001:4:-:d2cad555", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:2:-:27220ec4", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:3:-:0494063c", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:4:-:46c5925a"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_002:loc_001:3:-:6dc04883", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:1:-:fea3451b", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:2:-:6d9f5559"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_133038_c527e317", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 7, "retrieved": 3, "store_total": 20}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "turn_index": 6, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:36:19.355893+00:00", "player_text": "村里孩子发生什么了", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "艾拉放下手中的药草，神情略显忧虑。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "最近村里的几个孩子染上了怪咳，夜里咳得喘不过气。我试过普通的止咳草，但毫无效果。只有迷雾森林深处的银叶草才能缓解症状……可那地方太危险了，我一个草药师不敢独自前去。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "艾拉向玩家说明村中孩童患怪咳，急需银叶草治疗，但因迷雾森林危险而无法亲自前往。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:world_bible:-:-:-:-:e080a416", "20260315_133038_c527e317:location:-:loc_001:-:-:278b9587", "20260315_133038_c527e317:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:cde9ba91", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_001:loc_001:4:-:d2cad555", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_001:loc_001:5:-:cf18f4ff", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:3:-:0494063c", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:4:-:46c5925a", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:5:-:01b1fc12"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:1:-:fea3451b", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_002:loc_001:3:-:6dc04883", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:2:-:6d9f5559"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_133038_c527e317", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "doc_type": ["memory",