{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "turn_index": 7, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:37:26.461504+00:00", "player_text": "我没有找到银叶草", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "艾拉听到你的话，轻轻叹了口气，手指无意识地摩挲着药草篮的边缘。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "唉……迷雾森林深处确实危险重重。不过，如果你愿意再试一次，我听说银叶草多生长在毒蛛巢穴附近的石缝中——或许和那些毒蜘蛛出没的地方重合。若你顺路采集，对孩子们就是莫大的恩情了。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家告知艾拉未能找到银叶草，艾拉表示理解，并提示银叶草可能与毒蜘蛛巢穴位置接近，鼓励玩家再次尝试。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:world_bible:-:-:-:-:e080a416", "20260315_133038_c527e317:location:-:loc_001:-:-:278b9587", "20260315_133038_c527e317:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:cde9ba91", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_001:loc_001:4:-:d2cad555", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_001:loc_001:5:-:cf18f4ff", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_001:loc_001:6:-:4eb19a87", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:4:-:46c5925a", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:5:-:01b1fc12", "20260315_133038_c527e317:summary:-:-:6:-:7d0c3e49"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_007:loc_001:1:-:fea3451b", "20260315_133038_c527e317:memory:npc_002:loc_001:3:-:6dc04883"], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_133038_c527e317", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e317", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_133038_c527e